# Skill Routing

- When implementing a feature, fix, or code change, load the `implementing-changes` skill
- When exploring or onboarding to the codebase, load the `exploring-codebase` skill
- When debugging an issue or fixing a bug, load the `debugging-issues` skill
- When verifying changes work correctly, load the `verifying-changes` skill
- When preparing a commit or pull request, load the `preparing-pull-requests` skill
- When reviewing code for quality, load the `reviewing-code` skill
- When assessing code for security vulnerabilities, load the `reviewing-security` skill
